<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>For example, the following code:</p>

<pre><code>$request = new \Zend\Http\PhpEnvironment\Request;
$route = new \Zend\Mvc\Router\Http\Literal('');
$route-&gt;match($request, strlen($request-&gt;getBaseUrl()));
</code></pre>

<p>Will raise the following error:</p>

<pre><code>Fatal error: Uncaught PHP error with message: 'strpos(): Empty delimiter' in ... /Zend/Mvc/Router/Http/Literal.php:99
</code></pre>

<p>It is possible to workaround this problem with an empty Regex route.</p>

